OL,5, Many people may be suffering from an   
OL,6, undiagnosed and misunderstood bowel    
OL,7, condition, according to the charity    
OL,8, Guts UK.                               
OL,10,FMicroscopic colitis is an inflammation 
OL,11,Fof the large bowel and causes frequent 
OL,12,Fwatery diarrhoea, stomach pain, faecal 
OL,13,Fincontinence, fatigue and weight loss. 
OL,15,FAbout 17,000 people are diagnosed each 
OL,16,Fyear in the UK, but experts say the    
OL,17,Freal number is likely to be higher.    
OL,19,FSome standard tests for inflammatory   
OL,20,Fbowel conditions do not spot it.       
